Package: dreamlet
Type: Package
Title: Perform differential expression analysis on multi-sample single cell datasets using linear (mixed) models
Version: 0.0.32
Date: 2021-02-22
Authors@R: person("Gabriel", "Hoffman", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="gabriel.hoffman@mssm.edu")
Description: Dreamlet performs differential expression analysis on multi-sample single cell datasets using linear (mixed) models. The software is optimized for parallel processing and accessing large datasets using SingleCellExperiment backed by DelayedArray data.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/GabrielHoffman/dreamlet
BugReports: https://github.com/GabrielHoffman/dreamlet/issues
